  "title": "Quality Control Tester",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Performing incoming material tests, in-process inspection, and final goods product testing.</li><li>Understanding of cable standards and performing the tests according to international specifications.</li><li>Preparation of sample requirements based on customer’s required specifications.</li><li>Preparation of technical reports.</li><li>Planning and implementing performance improvement and quality assurance programs.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>A team player</li><li>Good communication skills</li><li>Positive work attitude</li><li>Job rotation involved to learn and process different QC test machines and procedures</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>ITE or Diploma. Fresh Grads welcome. Engineering experience is a plus.</li><li>Night shift availability is a bonus.</li></ul>",
