    "description": "<p>Keystone Cable is a homegrown, cable manufacturing business for more than 30 years. Our cables are used in iconic infrastructure projects in Singapore and overseas. At Keystone Cable, our employees are valuable to us. We are convinced that recruiting the right people and developing them on a right career path are vital for the future success of our company.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We were conferred the Human Capital Partner award by the Singapore government in recognition of our continuing efforts to develop our people at Keystone. We are proud that ~70% of our staff have been at Keystone for at least 5 years.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As the company grows, we are investing into smart factory and automation technologies and there will be plenty of opportunities to learn and grow with us.</p>",
